**To Reproduce**
Steps to reproduce the behavior:
1. clone git repo https://github.com/vsg-dev/vsgFramework
2. enter the directory where the repo has been cloned
3. run cmake -B ../vsgFramework-build && cmake --build ../vsgFramework-build
4. See error

**Expected behavior**
The build should not fail

**Platform (please complete the following information):**
 - OS: openSUSE Leap
 - Version 15.3
